<plot>We all know that Nero Wolfe is a real gourmet. Every week McLeod, a farmer, carries to him a parcel of just picked maize-cobs. But one week he can't come and the boy he sends is murdered at the back of the Rusterman Restaurant. Worse still the cobs are not just picked as they should.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?393212</url></doc>
